Model: Eight Warranty: 10 years Capacity: Brews up to 40oz (eight 5oz cups) Dimensions: 13.5" deep x 9" wide x 14" tall
Ratio Eight changes everything with precision brewing technique, top-quality construction, and a design that will elevate any environment for years to come. Each machine is hand assembled and tested in Portland, Oregon. That Eight has a powerful 1600 watt heating element in 110 (US & Canada) or 220 volt. Eight's carafe holds Chemex paper filters or Able Kone stainless steel filter.
